definition: abbr. for Uighur 維吾爾|维吾尔[Wei2 wu2 er3]/surname Wei
to preserve/to maintain/to hold together/dimension/vitamin (abbr. for 維生素|维生素[wei2 sheng1 su4])

sentences.english: The geology effect of 3-D seismic exploration in HK area, Jianghan region is presented in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 本文主要介绍江汉HK地区三维地震勘探的地质效果。

sentences.english: The three-dimensional object recognition is an important topic in computer vision research.
sentences.chinese: 三维物体识别是计算机视觉研究的一项重要课题。

sentences.english: Methods Two-dimensional ultrasound images scanning by free-hand were reconstructed stereoscopically in 39 patients with different diseases.
sentences.chinese: 方法采用本方法对39例患者进行了三维图像重建。

sentences.english: Three-dimensional movie changed a lot over the decades.
sentences.chinese: 三维立体电影在过去几十年中有了很大变化。

sentences.english: They are three-dimensional and they have feelings attached.
sentences.chinese: 这是三维的，而且是带有情感色彩的。

sentences.english: The results show that the vortex motion is unstable for small three-dimensional disturbances in the separated wake of a circular cylinder.
sentences.chinese: 结果表明，圆柱分离尾迹中的旋涡存在三维不稳定性。

sentences.english: Urban planning from two-dimensional arrangement to three-dimensional planning began long time ago.
sentences.chinese: 城市规划由平面的布置转向三维的规划，历史源远。

sentences.english: In this article, atom-pairs of compounds, which include abundant three-dimensional information of molecules, were calculated.
sentences.chinese: 采用原子对空间距离法表征化合物的三维结构信息。

sentences.english: A three-dimensional model for studying the surface shape of the rolls textured by laser beam is set up.
sentences.chinese: 建立了一种研究激光刻花轧辊表面形貌的三维模型。

sentences.english: Innovative, yet proven, SolidWorks software is the standard in 3D.
sentences.chinese: 创新至今，证实了烧窝是三维的标准。

sentences.english: A kind of Boolean operational method based on a three-dimensional grid model was proposed.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一种基于三维网格模型的布尔运算方法。

sentences.english: This paper pays attention to the application of 3D segmentation technology to plastic surgery.
sentences.chinese: 研究三维分割技术在医学整形领域的应用。

sentences.english: A model and its formula of 3-D 10-node mapped infinite element for intercalations in rock engineering are proposed.
sentences.chinese: 提出三维10结点映射夹层无限元模型及相应算式。

sentences.english: The all new collection from Blood Stream, with a 3D concertina background.
sentences.chinese: 新收集的所有从血液流，它具有三维手风琴的背景。

sentences.english: Based on above works, the three-dimension localization algorithm is proposed.
sentences.chinese: 并在基础上，提出了目标三维定位算法。
